# Summary
Plotline is a digital adoption platform that enables product and marketing teams to configure in-app nudges for improved feature adoption and conversions. This integration allows streaming event data from Amplitude to Plotline to create personalized in-app campaigns based on user behavior, with setup requiring a Plotline account and API key.

